{"tid":106924,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個兄弟姊妹做既賤野","createTime":"2017-02-04T05:25:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-04T10:48:50.000Z","uid":21001,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"42291309fee1ffede93ae46a01b7928bbecc4e16","tid":106924,"uid":21001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T05:25:40.000Z","msg":"有次同屋企人出街食完飯 我急屎急到仆街 <br />\n返到去諗住去解決之際 <br />\n我妹死都要去先 話自己急尿 好快屙完比我 <br />\n咁我心諗佢屙尿好快姐咪讓佢先囉<br />\n佢入左去一陣我已經係咁催佢問佢得未 <br />\n之後條粉腸話 <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">哎呀 唔小心屙左啲屎添</span></span> 我真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n明明佢都急屎又扮曬急尿去先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好撚狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a12f0a7fc0c347fd50899a2bf4ddf63a7eb53ab7","tid":106924,"uid":1582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T05:31:34.000Z","msg":"飲益力多昆鳩我<br />\n話飲到去個樽寫住 乳酸菌 嗰度就唔好再飲<br />\n再飲就好多菌<br />\n叫我飲到嗰度俾佢似 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f23577a25dc51475ea440ccd7b3043502d60abf","tid":106924,"uid":30471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T05:32:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢夜訓 跟手嘈醒佢去飲早茶<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e909f232a4be5386e67b43e2b5069c7dccf9609","tid":106924,"uid":71742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T05:35:09.000Z","msg":"沖沖下涼熄鳩沖涼房盞燈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"754435cd3709558f8f6b8daf9f254aa97a36cd50","tid":106924,"uid":6058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T08:17:42.000Z","msg":"影佢瞓覺相放上ig/fb<br />\n再tag佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b035b98c95f8600bb1ddd29336031083b87e344c","tid":106924,"uid":26937,"like":0,"dis